# Canonical parent works reused by specific bibliography references.
#
# Keep whole books, proceedings, journals, and other container-level creative works here when
# chapters, papers, or sections cite them via `schema:isPartOf`. This file is for reusable
# publication metadata, not for lesson-facing citations with page ranges or URLs; those concrete
# references belong in `05-references.ttl`.
@prefix schema: <https://schema.org/> .
@prefix dibs: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/vocab#> .
@prefix ref: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/ref/> .
@prefix person: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/person/> .
@prefix org: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/org/> .
@prefix work: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/work/> .
@prefix usage: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/usage/> .

